title: GRMLN "Before December (You're Alive)"
description:
“Before December (You’re Alive)” is an original song from Converse Rubber Tracks artist GRMLN, aka Yoodoo Park, Californian by way of Kyoto. The song is part of Converse Rubber Tracks’ holiday music EP, Noise To the World 2, which was mastered by Grammy-nominated engineer Mike Bozzi. 

Produced and mixed by: GRMLN
Music and Lyrics By: Yoodoo Park 
Mastered by: Mike Bozzi at Bernie Grundman
